messages.title: PUTTING AYRESOME FIRST
messages.content: Dear resident, Your Labour team called round today to discuss our plans for the future of Ayresome and for Middlesbrough. If you have an issue you would like us to look into, please don't hesitate to get in touch. Best wishes, DAVE, BERNIE, DENISE, ANDY AND THE LABOUR TEAM
